{"tid":1738372,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"環保署10月分區二噁英濃度數值未見上升","createTime":"2019-11-19T08:30:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T09:53:39.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2bb1a3a8ed51700b648a4ad3ade1571301065e44","tid":1738372,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T08:30:10.000Z","msg":"環保署公布10月在中西區和荃灣區空氣中二噁英的濃度。根據數據顯示，中西區監測站在10月10日，錄得二噁英平均濃度為每立方米0.008皮克，與以往3個月的數值相同。而10月3日荃灣監測站錄得二噁英平均濃度為每立方米0.011皮克，比上一個月少。<br />\n<br />\n警方近月大量使用催淚彈，外界關注會否釋放二噁英。環保署早前回覆查詢時表示，本港現時沒有空氣中二噁英的濃度指引，但過去3年本港錄得的二噁英濃度，遠低於加拿大安大略省的二噁英每立方米0.1皮克，和日本每立方米0.6皮克的指標。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1493237-20191119.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1493237-20191119.htm&d=U%2B24RsvDmKluq6DDuV4MqhVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=850a65ea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1493237-20191119.htm&h=a6df4f42\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1493237-20191119.htm</a>"},{"pid":"fa3bcf3c6311bcffeff9760122c47e345e49c1f7","tid":1738372,"uid":79793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T08:31:15.000Z","msg":"全部都係我嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02636a6f4ef50f463dc3f1a03570e5050d632075","tid":1738372,"uid":61484,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T08:33:12.000Z","msg":"太遲澄清<br />\n個表已經算hea <br />\n就咁excel 出都懶，冇人信"},{"pid":"8a4d17ef7a713487a62a81207bfd82e52b938965","tid":1738372,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T08:35:42.000Z","msg":"風向都變咗<br />\n又點會同過去三個月相同<br />\n好心做假都俾少少誠意<br />\n當人智障?"},{"pid":"8e21b26d24184d37c9f9fd3d1686761a49f1928e","tid":1738372,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"02636a6f4ef50f463dc3f1a03570e5050d632075","tid":1738372,"uid":61484,"like":4,"